entities.name: workspaceGroup.workspace
entities.description: Represents a workspace management group capable of creating, updating, deleting, resuming, and suspending workspaces.

entities.name: workspace
entities.description: Represents an individual workspace instance within a workspace management group.

entities.name: WORKSPACE_NAME
entities.description: The name identifier for a workspace.

entities.name: WORKSPACE_ID
entities.description: The unique identifier for a specific workspace.

entities.name: DatabaseSchema

entities.name: DATABASE_NAME
entities.description: The name identifier for a database.

entities.name: connection.database
entities.description: Represents a database connection capable of creating, using, and dropping databases.

relationships.description: workspaceGroup.workspace creates a workspace with WORKSPACE_NAME.
workspaceGroup.workspace updates workspace identified by WORKSPACE_ID.
workspaceGroup.workspace deletes workspace identified by WORKSPACE_ID.
